import React from 'react';
import { 
  Container, Typography, Box, Paper, Grid, 
  Divider, Card, CardContent, Avatar 
} from '@mui/material';
import RestaurantIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Restaurant';
import LocalShippingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocalShipping';
import ThumbUpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ThumbUp';
import DevicesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Devices';
import MetaTags from '../seo/MetaTags';

const About = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 6 }}>
      <MetaTags 
        title="About FoodExpress - Our Story" 
        description="Learn about FoodExpress, our mission, and how we connect you with the best local restaurants."
      />
      
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box textAlign="center" mb={6}>
        <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" gutterBottom fontWeight="bold">
          About FoodExpress
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" sx={{ maxWidth: 700, mx: 'auto' }}>
          We're on a mission to make food delivery easy, fast, and delightful.
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      
      {/* Our Story Section */}
      <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center" mb={8}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Box component="img" 
            src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/600x400/?restaurant,food" 
            alt="Restaurant interior"
            sx={{ width: '100%', borderRadius: 2 }}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Typography variant="h4" component="h2" gutterBottom>
            Our Story
          </Typography>
          <Typography paragraph>
            FoodExpress was founded in 2023 with a simple idea: make it easy for people to order food from their favorite local restaurants. 
          </Typography>
          <Typography paragraph>
            What started as a small startup in San Francisco has quickly grown into a beloved service connecting hungry customers with amazing restaurants across the country.
          </Typography>
          <Typography>
            Our platform helps local businesses thrive while providing customers with convenient access to delicious food, delivered right to their doorstep.
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      
      {/* Our Values Section */}
      <Box textAlign="center" mb={6}>
        <Typography variant="h4" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          Our Values
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ maxWidth: 700, mx: 'auto' }} paragraph>
          At FoodExpress, we're guided by core principles that shape how we serve our customers, 
          restaurant partners, and communities.
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      
      <Grid container spacing={3} mb={8}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}>
                <RestaurantIcon />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h6" component="h3" gutterBottom>
                Quality First
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                We partner with restaurants that prioritize quality ingredients and exceptional taste, ensuring every meal is delicious.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}>
                <LocalShippingIcon />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h6" component="h3" gutterBottom>
                Fast Delivery
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                We're committed to delivering your food promptly, ensuring it arrives fresh and at the perfect temperature.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}>
                <ThumbUpIcon />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h6" component="h3" gutterBottom>
                Customer Satisfaction
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Your happiness is our priority. We go above and beyond to ensure a seamless ordering experience every time.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Card sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}>
            <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}>
                <DevicesIcon />
              </Avatar>
              <Typography variant="h6" component="h3" gutterBottom>
                Easy Technology
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Our platform is designed to be intuitive and hassle-free, making food ordering a pleasure rather than a chore.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      
      {/* Our Team Section */}
      <Box mb={8}>
        <Typography variant="h4" component="h2" textAlign="center" gutterBottom>
          Our Team
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" textAlign="center" sx={{ maxWidth: 700, mx: 'auto' }} paragraph>
          Meet the passionate people behind FoodExpress who are dedicated to connecting you with great food.
        </Typography>
        
        <Grid container spacing={4} mt={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar 
                src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/100x100/?portrait,woman" 
                sx={{ width: 120, height: 120, mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}
              />
              <Typography variant="h6">Sarah Johnson</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="primary.main" gutterBottom>Founder & CEO</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                With 15 years in the restaurant industry, Sarah brings insider knowledge and passion to FoodExpress.
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar 
                src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/100x100/?portrait,man" 
                sx={{ width: 120, height: 120, mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}
              />
              <Typography variant="h6">Michael Chen</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="primary.main" gutterBottom>CTO</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Michael leads our tech team, ensuring the platform is fast, secure, and user-friendly.
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Avatar 
                src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/100x100/?portrait,person" 
                sx={{ width: 120, height: 120, mx: 'auto', mb: 2 }}
              />
              <Typography variant="h6">Olivia Martinez</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="primary.main" gutterBottom>Head of Operations</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                Olivia ensures smooth delivery operations and maintains our high standards with restaurant partners.
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      
      {/* Join Us Section */}
      <Paper 
        sx={{ 
          p: 4, 
          textAlign: 'center',
          background: 'linear-gradient(rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.05), rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.1))',
          borderRadius: 4
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h4" component="h2" gutterBottom>
          Join Our Growing Team
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          We're always looking for talented individuals who are passionate about food, technology, and customer service.
        </Typography>
        <Box sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
            Current Openings:
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={2} justifyContent="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <Paper sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
                <Typography variant="subtitle1">Delivery Operations Manager</Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <Paper sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
                <Typography variant="subtitle1">Senior Frontend Developer</Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <Paper sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
                <Typography variant="subtitle1">Restaurant Relations Specialist</Typography>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Paper>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default About;
